base_text:
name "phyto manager"

-- power
every 1 ticks do
    input fe:: from cube
    output fe:: to _ -- this is the base phyto variable. just 1 char long to reduce visual clutter as all phytos will have this variable
end
    
-- supply phytos with base items
every 200 ticks do
    -- base fluids and phyto-gro input
    input fluid:: from sink
    input phytogro from fertilizer
    -- base output to all types of pytogenic insulators
    output fluid:: to _
    output 64 to each _
end
seed_text_template:
--{seed} seeds
every 20 ticks do
    input {seed}_seeds from seed_chest
    output 4 retain 4 {seed}_seeds to each {seed}
    forget
    input from {seed} slots 2-4
    output {seed}_seeds to seed_chest
    output {seed}_essence to essence_chest
end

--{seed} seeds
every 20 ticks do
    input {seed}_seeds from seed_chest

    forget
    input from {seed} slots 2-4
